<h1>Resource Centre</h1><p class="halfbelow">Containing over 5,000 books, periodicials and videos devoted to the visual arts, the AGW Resource Centre is open to the public by appointment only. Contact <a href="mailto:nmccabe@agw.ca" target="_blank"><strong>Nicole McCabe</strong></a>, 519-977-0013 ext 134, to schedule a visit.</p><div id="TOOLS" style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">var object = SHARETHIS.addEntry({ title:'Resource+Centre', icon:'http://www.agw.ca/showimage/101-1/150', summary: 'Art Gallery of Windsor' }, {button:true});</script><p style='margin-top: 3px;'><b><a href='http://newsletters.agw.ca/?p=subscribe&id=1' target='_blank_sub'>Subscribe to AGW E-Mail Updates</a></b></p></div>   </div>
